{"tid":2159213,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"你地平時點樣叉電話電？","createTime":"2020-08-16T07:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T07:14:39.000Z","uid":178187,"like":129,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"a8bf4640eb062d6972095eacad366645dfd04301","tid":2159213,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:42:18.000Z","msg":"我諗通常都係臨訓前充<br />\n<br />\n但有人講過叉到100%會好hurt電<br />\n最好就係30/40%叉到80%<br />\n<br />\n想問下你地平時點樣叉？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />臨訓前沖，由幾/十幾%充到108<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 30/40%充到80"},{"pid":"398eb548456fcbe7a8861523a22f7eb69a650f34","tid":2159213,"uid":178187,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:43:06.000Z","msg":"由幾/十幾%充到100%"},{"pid":"b23629d29036a88783bf6b85d622fdad5e521597","tid":2159213,"uid":256804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:45:12.000Z","msg":"通常叉到97%"},{"pid":"0f141b67e40fb84849ead269db8372c7b0ccd653","tid":2159213,"uid":27416,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:46:14.000Z","msg":"新手機三日香"},{"pid":"9377a01ad8f3a0db8b7ec2237507d4334b516105","tid":2159213,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b23629d29036a88783bf6b85d622fdad5e521597","tid":2159213,"uid":256804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:45:12.000Z","msg":"通常叉到97%"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:46:20.000Z","msg":"咁跌到幾多先開始叉？"},{"pid":"e2ba2213bca22d1b36698f2237ccd76c3d9fe1b3","tid":2159213,"uid":256804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9377a01ad8f3a0db8b7ec2237507d4334b516105","tid":2159213,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b23629d29036a88783bf6b85d622fdad5e521597","tid":2159213,"uid":256804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:45:12.000Z","msg":"通常叉到97%"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:46:20.000Z","msg":"咁跌到幾多先開始叉？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:46:52.000Z","msg":"40幾"},{"pid":"d2de6fa5866a798a78399c534f7dd7e268fad2f5","tid":2159213,"uid":151534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:46:53.000Z","msg":"30-50%"},{"pid":"3d820f44f2b236431f4b680ec7a979d6232dd3df","tid":2159213,"uid":325243,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:47:37.000Z","msg":"108%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad075b2e001c2145b36d94da732a7647cc66a4c","tid":2159213,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:47:41.000Z","msg":"差唔滿就用先傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時到15%先會差滿佢"},{"pid":"15318fe165d0107da4a744e22fd4b1a8c0217f0e","tid":2159213,"uid":18484,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:48:30.000Z","msg":"係公司屋企有電就長插"},{"pid":"06fa72de595494a8fcd2044ddfa2853d2a3efaff","tid":2159213,"uid":178187,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:48:44.000Z","msg":"手機可唔可以叉通宵？同你破解4大叉電謠言<br />\n<br />\n1. 手機不可通宵充電<br />\n<br />\n不少人都認為手機通宵充電會使電池超岀負荷，嚴重的，甚至會引致爆炸。其實，現在的鋰電池技術會讓電池在充滿後便自動停止充電，因此毋須擔心。<br />\n<br />\n2. 等到完全沒電時才充電<br />\n<br />\n現時的鋰電池壽命是以周期計算的，電力從 0% 充電到 100%代表1 個周期。若手機電量由 90% 充電至 100% ，便是使用了 1/10 個周期。而目前鋰電池的周期平均約為 300 至 500 次之間。因此，為了避免浪費一個完整的周期，最好是每天多次為手機充電。專家也提及到，只要把電量保持在40%到80%之間，便更有效延長電池的壽命。"},{"pid":"c4010125a32d8b7d19dc0d1070851cb4e24d0dc0","tid":2159213,"uid":25169,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:49:41.000Z","msg":"用念力叉電"},{"pid":"56bfbf520e4fc514fbc1c4c9bc4764eb15da3960","tid":2159213,"uid":53122,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:49:57.000Z","msg":"鍾意點差都得<br />\n通常舊電打柴前<br />\n你已經頂唔順部垃圾機慢"},{"pid":"ae125